and Ms. Cha is being investigated
for the case that killed Hwa-jin's mom.

553
00:41:05,212 --> 00:41:07,465
Witness or not, it doesn't matter.

554
00:41:07,548 --> 00:41:08,632
The fact is

555
00:41:09,467 --> 00:41:10,759
that I'm her husband.

556
00:41:10,843 --> 00:41:11,844
And

557
00:41:13,137 --> 00:41:15,514
that I can't leave her there alone.

558
00:41:16,223 --> 00:41:17,224
President-elect.

559
00:41:17,808 --> 00:41:19,101
