577
00:42:13,364 --> 00:42:16,575
Come on, I'm sure you have more to say.

578
00:42:16,659 --> 00:42:19,578
The online forum is being bombarded
by curious viewers.

579
00:42:20,412 --> 00:42:22,206
I already said in the interview

580
00:42:22,289 --> 00:42:25,251
that I came on the show
to catch the hit-and-run offender.

581
00:42:25,334 --> 00:42:27,503
I don't care as long as
they catch the offender.

582
00:42:29,296 --> 00:42:32,383
If Ms. Cha is the culprit,
that's not the end.

583
00:42:33,259 --> 00:42:34,468
It could be the beginning.

584
00:42:39,098 --> 00:42:40,766
The beginning? What do you mean?

585
00:42:41,433 --> 00:42:43,686
President-elect could get involved too.

586
00:42:45,521 --> 00:42:47,773
Do you think he really didn't know
that his wife

587
00:42:48,857 --> 00:42:49,942
killed your mother?

588
00:42:54,780 --> 00:42:56,407
