589
00:43:00,661 --> 00:43:02,079
or been her accomplice.

590
00:43:06,875 --> 00:43:08,002
That's impossible.

591
00:43:08,085 --> 00:43:11,046
Ms. Eom passed away
a week before the election.

592
00:43:11,714 --> 00:43:15,175
