so I called you.

613
00:44:39,009 --> 00:44:41,887
Gosh, no.
Think of it as my thank-you gift.

614
00:44:42,554 --> 00:44:44,807
You tipped off
Ms. Cha's hit-and-run to me,

615
00:44:44,890 --> 00:44:47,935
