661
00:48:11,555 --> 00:48:15,350
Do the laundry, clean the house,
and wash the dishes.

662
00:48:16,476 --> 00:48:20,439
You can call yourself an adult
only when you can do all those yourself.

663
00:48:20,522 --> 00:48:22,566
Do you have more to nag?

664
00:48:22,649 --> 00:48:24,318
