677
00:49:03,940 --> 00:49:04,983
Are you going somewhere?

678
00:49:06,526 --> 00:49:08,445
It was my dream.

679
00:49:09,821 --> 00:49:10,864
You know,

680
00:49:11,406 --> 00:49:14,493
