share your thoughts with us.

805
01:00:37,342 --> 01:00:38,217
To your position.

806
01:00:38,301 --> 01:00:39,469
Get in your position.

807
01:00:43,014 --> 01:00:44,974
-Don't push.
-Wait.

808
01:00:45,058 --> 01:00:47,018
-Say something.
-Move aside.

809
01:00:47,101 --> 01:00:50,063
Ms. Cha is being investigated
for Eom's hit-and-run.

810
01:00:50,146 --> 01:00:51,731
How do you feel about it?

811
01:00:52,231 --> 01:00:53,274
She's just a witness.

812
01:00:53,358 --> 01:00:56,402
Were you aware of her involvement
in Eom Sun-jeong's death?

813
01:00:56,486 --> 01:00:58,196
Some suggest it was planned murder

814
01:00:58,279 --> 01:01:00,657
to silence her
about the illegitimate daughter.

815
01:01:01,658 --> 01:01:04,035
I already said
she was brought in as a witness.

816
01:01:04,118 --> 01:01:07,038
Some even suggest
that you instigated the murder of Eom.

817
01:01:08,206 --> 01:01:10,625
Refrain from groundless assumptions
and reports.

818
01:01:10,708 --> 01:01:13,419
"She's just a witness,
it's a groundless assumption."

819
01:01:13,503 --> 01:01:17,131
Don't you think you're suggesting
guidelines on the investigation

820
01:01:17,215 --> 01:01:19,425
just by saying that
as the president-elect?

821
01:01:20,009 --> 01:01:22,512
The cops working on the case
could feel pressured

822
01:01:22,595 --> 01:01:25,848
just from your presence here,
where Ms. Cha is being investigated.

823
01:01:25,932 --> 01:01:27,934
I'm not trying to pressure them

824
01:01:28,768 --> 01:01:31,062
or suggest guidelines
on the investigation.

825
01:01:31,145 --> 01:01:34,565
I just want to stay
as close as possible to my wife.

826
01:01:35,608 --> 01:01:38,736
If that in itself is wrong,
it can't be helped.

827
01:01:38,820 --> 01:01:39,946
I will have to

828
01:01:40,780 --> 01:01:41,781
commit the wrong.

829
01:01:41,864 --> 01:01:44,617
Are you saying
you'll blatantly ignore the people?

830
01:01:44,701 --> 01:01:48,329
The people are raising suspicions
and are outraged.

831
01:01:48,413 --> 01:01:51,416
The allegations on an illegitimate child
and a hit-and-run.

832
01:01:51,499 --> 01:01:53,668
The people are
demanding your resignation.

833
01:01:57,755 --> 01:01:58,965
That anger.

834
01:01:59,882 --> 01:02:01,092
That fury.

835
01:02:02,593 --> 01:02:04,220
I'll accept wholly.

836
01:02:05,555 --> 01:02:07,140
But I won't turn away

837
01:02:08,099 --> 01:02:10,143
from my wife out of fear for them.

838
01:02:10,226 --> 01:02:11,227
If

839
01:02:11,310 --> 01:02:14,689
she is in any way involved
in the hit-and-run case,

840
01:02:15,565 --> 01:02:17,442
do you intend to step down?

841
01:02:18,401 --> 01:02:20,403
Will you be responsible for your claim

842
01:02:20,486 --> 01:02:22,947
and put your presidency on the line?

843
01:02:25,283 --> 01:02:28,786
President-elect has nothing to do
with the hit-and-run.

844
01:02:34,625 --> 01:02:37,795
It's currently under investigation.
How can you be sure?

845
01:02:41,716 --> 01:02:42,759
Because I am

846
01:02:44,093 --> 01:02:45,052
the culprit.

847
01:02:50,767 --> 01:02:52,727
The person who killed Eom Sun-jeong…

848
01:02:55,354 --> 01:02:56,689
is me.

849
01:03:51,160 --> 01:03:52,370
Su-yeon.

850
01:03:52,954 --> 01:03:55,790
Tell me if you're involved
with Chairman Yang in any way.

851
01:03:56,290 --> 01:03:57,917
This is the last chance.

852
01:03:58,000 --> 01:03:59,585
If you mess around again,

853
01:03:59,669 --> 01:04:01,462
then I'll reveal this.

854
01:04:02,046 --> 01:04:05,925
The person standing on the receiving end
of your special act isn't Yang Hoon.

855
01:04:06,008 --> 01:04:07,718
It's Su-yeon.

856
01:04:08,386 --> 01:04:09,846
If the investigation

857
01:04:09,929 --> 01:04:12,515
reveals that I or my wife
were involved in the fire,

858
01:04:12,598 --> 01:04:14,225
-Honey!
-I will step down

859
01:04:14,308 --> 01:04:16,227
from my president-elect position

860
01:04:16,310 --> 01:04:17,895
immediately.

861
